<Layout title="Invoice Calculation Fix" description="Resolved invoice calculation rounding inconsistencies">
  <h1>Invoice Calculation Fix</h1>

  <h2>Issue</h2>
  <p>Invoice totals were occasionally off by a few cents due to inconsistent rounding during tax and discount calculations.</p>

  <h2>Resolution</h2>
  <p>Updated the calculation logic to ensure consistent rounding at each step. All monetary values now round to two decimal places using banker's rounding (round half to even).</p>

  <h2>Impact</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Eliminates discrepancies in invoice totals.</li>
    <li>Improves customer trust and reduces support inquiries.</li>
    <li>Ensures compliance with financial reporting standards.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Technical Changes</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Implemented standardized rounding function across all calculation modules.</li>
    <li>Added unit tests for edge cases in tax and discount calculations.</li>
    <li>Updated documentation for financial calculation procedures.</li>
  </ul>

  <hr>

  <p><a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}bugfixes/`}>‚Üê Back to Bug Fixes</a> | <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}`}>Home</a></p>
</Layout>
